1275
01:29:47,174 --> 01:29:49,927
...they're hanging our black Christians
from trees.

1276
01:29:50,094 --> 01:29:53,389
This is the man that hates you.
He doesn't do anything for you.

1277
01:29:53,597 --> 01:29:55,933
He tells you to foam at
the mouth and sing...

1278
01:29:56,141 --> 01:29:59,978
...and hope for something in the hereafter.
We can have it right now.

1279
01:30:00,187 --> 01:30:02,439
- Come on down, 2:00.
- See you later.

1280
01:30:02,648 --> 01:30:05,859
<i>As-Salaam-Alaikum.</i>
That means, "Peace be unto you."

1281
01:30:06,068 --> 01:30:09,154
We have two children.
Carla, who's 2 1/2, and....

