01:31:21,018 --> 01:31:22,561
Is that you, brother?

1304
01:31:22,769 --> 01:31:26,732
Now, this is exactly what I'm talking
about, the slave mentality...

1305
01:31:26,899 --> 01:31:30,068
...the slave mind. This brother and I,
