01:31:40,078 --> 01:31:42,164
Stand up, brother. Come on.

1311
01:31:42,331 --> 01:31:45,250
Ha-ha-ha. The brother's a little shy.

1312
01:31:45,417 --> 01:31:47,586
Come on, brother. Give me a hug.

1313
01:31:49,630 --> 01:31:52,508
That's all right, brother. That's all right.

1314
01:31:52,674 --> 01:31:54,635
Look, he's still got his hair fried.

1315
01:31:54,843 --> 01:31:57,596
That's the slave mind.
That's the slave mind.

1316
01:31:57,804 --> 01:32:00,933
Red, that's the best preacher hype
I ever did hear.

1317
01:32:01,141 --> 01:32:03,018
No hype, brother. It's the truth.

1318
01:32:03,227 --> 01:32:05,270
Come back to the temple and hear more.

1319
01:32:05,479 --> 01:32:07,272
