01:38:05,797 --> 01:38:07,883
Brother Malcolm, this is Sister Betty.

1422
01:38:08,091 --> 01:38:10,802
She lectures our Muslim women
on hygiene and diet.

1423
01:38:11,011 --> 01:38:14,139
She stresses care for the body
and regular eating habits.

1424
01:38:14,431 --> 01:38:15,640
Good.

1425
01:38:15,807 --> 01:38:18,602
<i>- As-Salaam-Alaikum.
